<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #fcfcfc;
      color: #1a1a1a;
    }

    .wrapper {
      width: 100%;
      padding: 40px 0;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #ffffff;
      padding: 50px;
      border: 1px solid #eeeeee;
      border-radius: 24px;
    }

    .logo {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: 900;
      letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    p {
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #666666;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .order-card {
      background: #f8f8f8;
      padding: 25px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      margin: 30px 0;
    }

    .item-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 10px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eeeeee;
    }

    .item-name {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .item-price {
      font-weight: 800;
      font-size: 14px;
    }

    .total-row {
      padding-top: 20px;
      text-align: right;
      font-size: 20px;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .footer {
      margin-top: 50px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 11px;
      color: #aaaaaa;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="logo">
        <img src="https://dnshop.com.ar/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/logodnstyle.png" alt="DN shop"
          style="height: 100px; width: auto; display: block; margin: 0 auto;">
      </div>
      <h1>¡Gracias por tu compra!</h1>
      <p>Hola {{name}}, hemos recibido tu pedido #{{order_id}}. Estamos preparando tus productos con el mayor cuidado.
      </p>

      <div class="order-card">
        {{#each items}}
        <div class="item-row">
          <span class="item-name">{{name}} x{{quantity}}</span>
          <span class="item-price">${{price}}</span>
        </div>
        {{/each}}
        <div class="total-row">Total: ${{total}}</div>
      </div>

      <p style="font-size: 13px;">Recibirás otro correo cuando tu pedido esté en camino.</p>

      <div class="footer">
        DN shop STORE &copy; {{year}} | BUENOS AIRES, ARGENTINA
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>